  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "bc2f8338-36fb-4d7c-b822-f8d21639efe6",
    "name": "Votação API",
    "description": "A collection for the Votação API, providing endpoints to manage voting questions, register votes, and retrieve results.\n\n## Getting Started\n\nSet the `base_url` collection variable to your API host (default: `http://teste-votacao.lndo.site`) and the `api_key` variable to your API key. All requests automatically include the `x-api-key` header via the collection pre-request script.\n\n## Variables\n\n| Variable | Description | Default |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | Base URL of the API | `http://teste-votacao.lndo.site` |\n| `api_key` | API key for authentication | `voting-api-8f4b2c9e1a7d` |\n\n## Authentication\n\nAll requests require the `x-api-key` header, which is automatically injected at the collection level using the `{{api_key}}` variable.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "3596197"
  },
